These are Puzzles for 6x2 Level 8

.:: Puzzle 6x2-Level-8-1::.
City: liverpool, rome
There 2 different types of food: onion, orange
The people have 2 different hobbies: collecting, video-games
The people perfer 2 different movie-genres: fantasy, satire
The people's birthday is in 2 different months: september, july
There are 2 different nationalities: nigerian, american
1. the person who's hobby is collecting is the person watching satire movies##1
2. the person who's birthday is in july is somewhere to the right of the person eating orange##5
3. the person traveling to liverpool is on the far right##1
4. the person watching fantasy movies is on the left of the nigerian##1
5. the person who's hobby is collecting is not to the left of the person who's birthday is in july##8
6. the nigerian is not to the left of the person who's birthday is in july##8

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |      2      |
| City      | rome      | liverpool |
| Food          | orange      | onion       |
| Hobby         | video-games | collecting  |
| Movie-Genre   | fantasy     | satire      |
| Birthday   | september       | july      |
| Nationality         | american    | nigerian       |

