.:: Puzzle 6x2-Level-8-2::.
There 2 different types of food: grapefruit, zucchini
The people have 2 different hobbies: skydiving, writing
The people grow 2 different varities of flowers: sunflower, bellflower
The people prefer 2 different music-genres: pop, trance
There are 2 different favourite beverages: lemonade, almond-milk
2 different brands of cigars are smoked: bluemaster, oliveros
1. the person who growssunflower is not to the left of the person who's hobby is skydiving##8
2. the person who growsbellflower is not to the left of the person who's hobby is writing##8
3. the person drinking lemonade is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is writing##3
4. the oliveros-smoker is on the right of the person eating grapefruit##1
5. the person who growssunflower is not to the left of the fan of trance##8
6. the person eating zucchini is on the left or right of the person drinking lemonade##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |    2     |
| Food          | grapefruit | zucchini |
| Hobby         | skydiving  | writing  |
| Flower           | sunflower      | bellflower  |
| Music-Genre   | trance     | pop      |
| Beverage           | lemonade     | almond-milk    |
| Cigar     | bluemaster  | oliveros     |

